### Create a new Skill
POST http://localhost:5169/api/skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Comfortable with Linux CLI",
  "description": "Learn basic bash commands, file navigation, and permissions.",
  "status": 0
}

### Get all Skills
GET http://localhost:5169/api/skills

### Link Skill 2 as a prerequisite to Skill 1
POST http://localhost:5169/api/skills/1/prerequisites
Content-Type: application/json

### Check if Skill 1 can be started (Should return true because it has no prerequisites yet)
GET http://localhost:5169/api/skills/canStart/1

### Check if Skill 1 can be started again (Should return false because its prerequisite, Skill 2, is status 0 / Not Started)
GET http://localhost:5169/api/skills/canStart/1